</ul><p><img src="http://www.infoq.com/resource/articles/cpp-in-multi-device-enterprise/zh/resources/5.png;jsessionid=0F25FB8F112D1D3666AE87F1BAF3E8AA" alt="" _href="img://null" _p="true" /></p><p>为什么C++Builder XE3完美适用于多设备企业应用开发？ C++Builder XE3提供：</p><ul> 
